inlineContent.text: This method converts the object ID of each managed object in
to a permanent ID. Although the object will have a permanent ID, it will still respond positively to
until it is saved. Any object that already has a permanent ID is ignored.

Any object not already assigned to a store is assigned based on the same rules Core Data uses for assignment during a save operation (first writable store supporting the entity, and appropriate for the instance and its related items).
